results.title: What I Learned Dogsitting for New York City’s Opulent Elite
results.text: In a city of yawning class inequality, some side hustles let you glimpse how the other half lives.

results.title: The Virtual Vet Will See You Meow
results.text: Veterinary telemedicine could help more pet owners access much-needed care and put anxious animals at ease, but challenges remain.
